title: Mastercard Rises 3%
text:
Mastercard Rises 3%

Stock Markets 32 minutes ago (Oct 24, 2019 12:03PM ET)

© Reuters. Mastercard Rises 3% Investing.com - Mastercard (NYSE: ) rose by 3.10% to trade at $268.81 by 12:01 (16:01 GMT) on Thursday on the NYSE exchange. The volume of Mastercard shares traded since the start of the session was 1.67M. Mastercard has traded in a range of $263.69 to $268.81 on the day. The stock has traded at $280.4400 at its highest and $258.5100 at its lowest during the past seven days.
